1
00:00:06,333 --> 00:00:08,367
Stop this madness!

2
00:00:08,500 --> 00:00:09,333
[THUDS]

3
00:00:09,467 --> 00:00:11,100
Is it good, Thea?

4
00:00:11,233 --> 00:00:13,567
Does it feel good to take
someone else's spouse?

5
00:00:13,700 --> 00:00:14,400
[THUDS]

6
00:00:14,533 --> 00:00:15,533
[GRUNTS]

7
00:00:15,667 --> 00:00:17,600
You even took my spouse from me!

8
00:00:17,733 --> 00:00:18,633
If you weren't useless,

9
00:00:18,767 --> 00:00:20,833
I wouldn't look
for someone else!

10
00:00:20,967 --> 00:00:22,800
You are such a loser!

11
00:00:22,933 --> 00:00:25,233
I regret marrying you!

12
00:00:25,367 --> 00:00:27,300
I regret loving you!

13
00:00:27,433 --> 00:00:29,767
I regret ever knowing you!

14
00:00:29,900 --> 00:00:32,567
This house has been
rotting for a long time.

15
00:00:32,700 --> 00:00:34,967
Only now has the
stench come out.

16
00:00:35,133 --> 00:00:36,400
To hell with this house!

17
00:00:36,533 --> 00:00:40,133
This house and this family
deserve to burn

18
00:00:40,267 --> 00:00:42,633
because this place is hell
itself!

19
00:01:28,300 --> 00:01:30,567
The vows have been renewed.

20
00:01:31,533 --> 00:01:33,433
Mr. Torrecampo,

21
00:01:33,567 --> 00:01:35,367
you may now kiss your wife
again.

22
00:01:35,500 --> 00:01:39,800
[PENSIVE]

23
00:01:41,500 --> 00:01:43,333
[INTENSE]

24
00:01:46,200 --> 00:01:48,100
Stop this madness!

25
00:01:48,233 --> 00:01:49,067
[MUSIC CONTINUES]

26
00:01:49,200 --> 00:01:52,067
[BACKGROUND CHATTER]

27
00:02:06,433 --> 00:02:07,533
Marj, please, not here.

28
00:02:08,467 --> 00:02:09,200
[THUDS]

29
00:02:12,167 --> 00:02:13,633
This is exactly
where it should be!

30
00:02:13,800 --> 00:02:15,533
In front of everyone!

31
00:02:15,667 --> 00:02:19,767
On the day you chose to pretend
this family is solid!

32
00:02:19,900 --> 00:02:21,800
Marj, stop this!

33
00:02:21,933 --> 00:02:23,400
Please, don't do this on
this occasion,

34
00:02:23,533 --> 00:02:24,600
not in our home!

35
00:02:24,733 --> 00:02:26,533
This house is not a home!

36
00:02:28,300 --> 00:02:31,900
This house is a slaughterhouse
for those who trusted!

37
00:02:33,233 --> 00:02:34,900
This house is filthy

38
00:02:35,033 --> 00:02:38,033
because you let two pigs live
under one roof!

39
00:02:39,300 --> 00:02:40,333
You're impressive too, huh?

40
00:02:40,467 --> 00:02:42,600
Don't touch me!

41
00:02:42,733 --> 00:02:44,633
With all the houses
you've sold,

42
00:02:44,767 --> 00:02:47,500
I never thought you'd even list
my spouse as well!

43
00:02:48,700 --> 00:02:49,433
Marj, what is this?

44
00:02:49,567 --> 00:02:50,400
You're just embarrassing
yourself!

45
00:02:50,533 --> 00:02:51,267
What?

46
00:02:51,400 --> 00:02:53,067
Was your commission
not enough?

47
00:02:53,200 --> 00:02:56,933
That you even had to enter
my bed just to earn money?

48
00:02:57,067 --> 00:02:58,533
Was it good?

49
00:02:58,667 --> 00:03:00,033
Thea!

50
00:03:00,167 --> 00:03:02,667
Is it good to take
someone else's spouse?

51
00:03:05,133 --> 00:03:06,100
[CLAMORING]

52
00:03:10,033 --> 00:03:10,733
[CLAMORING CONTINUES]

53
00:03:10,867 --> 00:03:12,200
Marj! Marj! Stop it!

54
00:03:12,333 --> 00:03:13,400
Marj! Marj!

55
00:03:13,533 --> 00:03:14,800
- Marj!
- Come here!

56
00:03:14,933 --> 00:03:15,767
Marj!

57
00:03:15,900 --> 00:03:16,633
- Marj!
- Stop it!

58
00:03:16,767 --> 00:03:17,533
Marj!

59
00:03:25,833 --> 00:03:31,900
- Stop it, Marj!
- Marj, stop it!

60
00:03:32,033 --> 00:03:34,533
You animal! You demon!

61
00:03:34,667 --> 00:03:35,833
[SPEAKS IN VISAYAN LANGUAGE]

62
00:03:37,933 --> 00:03:38,633
Marj!

63
00:03:38,767 --> 00:03:39,933
Marj, stop it!

64
00:03:40,067 --> 00:03:42,367
Ask your spouse!

65
00:03:42,500 --> 00:03:43,500
Why are you doing this?

66
00:03:43,633 --> 00:03:44,533
On what basis?

67
00:03:44,667 --> 00:03:48,867
Ask her and your sibling
what they were doing

68
00:03:49,000 --> 00:03:50,767
behind our backs!

69
00:03:50,900 --> 00:03:51,600
Enough!

70
00:03:53,067 --> 00:03:54,700
Everyone inside!

71
00:03:55,667 --> 00:03:56,433
Guard!

72
00:03:56,567 --> 00:04:01,900
[SPEAKS IN VISAYAN LANGUAGE]

73
00:04:02,033 --> 00:04:03,000
You're going to pay
for what you did!

74
00:04:03,133 --> 00:04:04,133
Take them inside!

75
00:04:04,267 --> 00:04:04,933
Enough!

76
00:04:05,067 --> 00:04:06,900
- Take them inside!
- Enough!

77
00:04:07,033 --> 00:04:08,300
Let go of me!

78
00:04:12,700 --> 00:04:15,467
Let go of me! You animal!

79
00:04:15,600 --> 00:04:17,200
[INTENSE]

80
00:04:17,333 --> 00:04:18,267
I'm so sorry.

81
00:04:18,400 --> 00:04:19,400
Just a misunderstanding.

82
00:04:19,533 --> 00:04:20,867
I'm so sorry.

83
00:04:21,000 --> 00:04:22,000
Please, eat.

84
00:04:22,133 --> 00:04:22,867
[INTENSE]

85
00:04:23,000 --> 00:04:24,000
I'm so sorry.

86
00:04:29,033 --> 00:04:30,467
Yolly, please.

87
00:04:30,600 --> 00:04:32,233
Please erase those videos.

88
00:04:32,367 --> 00:04:34,433
Please, handle it.

89
00:04:34,567 --> 00:04:43,233
[INTENSE]

90
00:04:50,067 --> 00:04:52,200
Are you okay, Jas?

91
00:04:52,333 --> 00:04:53,633
Just tell me.

92
00:04:53,767 --> 00:04:56,900
So I can call the nurse
if you feel anything.

93
00:04:58,033 --> 00:05:03,100
I'm just a bit drained, Auntie,
but I'm okay.

94
00:05:04,600 --> 00:05:06,200
You know, you're really brave.

95
00:05:07,500 --> 00:05:08,833
I have to be, Auntie.

96
00:05:09,700 --> 00:05:14,633
I can't waste my mom's
sacrifices by giving up.

97
00:05:14,767 --> 00:05:17,833
They are really the reason
why I keep fighting.

98
00:05:19,733 --> 00:05:24,500
There are many things
I can't control.

99
00:05:25,900 --> 00:05:28,567
Like this, I can't do anything.

100
00:05:28,700 --> 00:05:30,100
There's so many uncertain
things.

101
00:05:31,467 --> 00:05:33,300
Like whether I'll recover.

102
00:05:34,100 --> 00:05:34,933
Or what?

103
00:05:36,167 --> 00:05:39,400
But they are my constant.

104
00:05:40,300 --> 00:05:44,733
Their support and love
for each other.

105
00:05:44,867 --> 00:05:48,267
As long as we're together,
I can endure it.

106
00:05:54,500 --> 00:05:56,533
You did not have any right

107
00:05:56,667 --> 00:06:00,333
to turn a private family moment
into a public spectacle.

108
00:06:00,467 --> 00:06:02,533
What are you angry about
to make such a scene?

109
00:06:02,667 --> 00:06:04,933
Why did you ruin my day?

110
00:06:05,067 --> 00:06:06,633
There was an earlier scandal.

111
00:06:08,867 --> 00:06:09,733
Marj, please,
this isn't necessary.

112
00:06:09,867 --> 00:06:10,800
It is necessary!

113
00:06:13,600 --> 00:06:15,900
[INTENSE]

114
00:06:18,367 --> 00:06:19,333
[THEA MOANING]

115
00:06:21,700 --> 00:06:22,833
[PAOLO GROANS]

116
00:06:26,900 --> 00:06:29,800
[MUSIC CONTINUES]

117
00:06:47,900 --> 00:06:50,767
That's what our spouse is doing,
Edward.

118
00:06:51,900 --> 00:06:52,800
[THUDS]

119
00:06:52,933 --> 00:06:53,567
Edward!

120
00:06:53,700 --> 00:06:55,733
[CLAMORING]

121
00:06:56,400 --> 00:06:57,000
Enough!

122
00:06:58,833 --> 00:07:00,367
What kind of sibling are you?

123
00:07:00,500 --> 00:07:02,233
You even took my spouse from me!

124
00:07:04,467 --> 00:07:05,467
What do you want?

125
00:07:12,967 --> 00:07:14,033
You.

126
00:07:14,200 --> 00:07:15,767
You're thinking it
the wrong way!

127
00:07:15,900 --> 00:07:17,433
You!

128
00:07:19,000 --> 00:07:21,000
Enough of your lies.

129
00:07:21,133 --> 00:07:22,500
I want to know everything!

130
00:07:23,533 --> 00:07:24,267
Everything!

131
00:07:25,200 --> 00:07:27,367
[SQUEALS]

132
00:07:27,500 --> 00:07:28,567
Edward?

133
00:07:28,700 --> 00:07:29,633
Edward!

134
00:07:40,167 --> 00:07:42,300
Look what you did, Marj!

135
00:07:42,433 --> 00:07:44,500
I didn't ruin this day.

136
00:07:45,300 --> 00:07:47,167
It was already ruined
before I arrived.

137
00:07:48,433 --> 00:07:51,367
I'm done trusting you
and this family!

138
00:07:55,300 --> 00:07:56,100
Marj, wait!

139
00:07:56,233 --> 00:07:57,967
Marj!

140
00:08:04,833 --> 00:08:10,933
Why did this happen to us,
to our children?

141
00:08:11,067 --> 00:08:15,300
How could we have let this
happen in our own home?

142
00:08:17,200 --> 00:08:19,000
[SOBBING]

143
00:08:20,000 --> 00:08:22,100
[INTENSE]

144
00:08:22,267 --> 00:08:23,533
Stop!

145
00:08:23,667 --> 00:08:25,533
Edward, you're hurting me!

146
00:08:26,400 --> 00:08:27,300
What are you doing?

147
00:08:32,833 --> 00:08:34,067
How long?

148
00:08:36,200 --> 00:08:38,200
How long have you
been fooling me?

149
00:08:39,933 --> 00:08:40,833
Answer me!

150
00:08:42,800 --> 00:08:43,767
Why, Edward?

151
00:08:44,733 --> 00:08:47,767
If I tell you, when it started,
will the pain lessen?

152
00:08:49,167 --> 00:08:51,067
Or do you just want to hear
details

153
00:08:51,200 --> 00:08:53,933
so you can feel
even more worthless?

154
00:08:56,367 --> 00:08:57,567
You have some nerve!

155
00:08:58,867 --> 00:09:03,167
I'm the one at fault now?

156
00:09:03,300 --> 00:09:05,433
Yes!

157
00:09:05,667 --> 00:09:06,600
If you weren't useless,

158
00:09:06,733 --> 00:09:08,400
I wouldn't look
for someone else!

159
00:09:09,367 --> 00:09:11,067
[DRAMATIC]

160
00:09:11,200 --> 00:09:12,733
You were such a loser!

161
00:09:17,433 --> 00:09:19,567
Marj, wait, let's talk.

162
00:09:19,700 --> 00:09:20,933
Don't touch me!

163
00:09:22,867 --> 00:09:25,200
You disgust me!

164
00:09:26,100 --> 00:09:28,333
Marj, please let me explain.

165
00:09:29,167 --> 00:09:31,800
What else is there to explain?

166
00:09:31,933 --> 00:09:33,267
You've been exposed!

167
00:09:34,833 --> 00:09:36,700
How long did you lie to me?

168
00:09:38,933 --> 00:09:40,867
Did you really love me?

169
00:09:42,967 --> 00:09:44,967
Did you ever loved me?

170
00:09:46,000 --> 00:09:49,867
Because if you loved me,
you wouldn't hurt me!

171
00:09:51,133 --> 00:09:52,400
You have no shame!

172
00:09:53,567 --> 00:09:56,233
You even went after
your sibling's spouse!

173
00:09:57,767 --> 00:10:00,867
While your sibling
has so much success,

174
00:10:01,000 --> 00:10:04,600
so many achievements,
while you achieved nothing!

175
00:10:04,767 --> 00:10:06,667
And you're dragging us down!

176
00:10:06,800 --> 00:10:07,700
That's not true!

177
00:10:10,633 --> 00:10:13,267
I give everything to you!

178
00:10:18,300 --> 00:10:19,267
Edward!

179
00:10:21,733 --> 00:10:25,133
Please stop fooling yourself!

180
00:10:27,267 --> 00:10:31,500
The security I need in a man,
you don't have it!

181
00:10:31,633 --> 00:10:34,100
I admit, I was weak.

182
00:10:34,233 --> 00:10:36,900
I gave in to temptation.

183
00:10:37,067 --> 00:10:38,233
But that's over.

184
00:10:38,367 --> 00:10:40,000
You're the one I love.

185
00:10:40,133 --> 00:10:40,900
I love you so much.

186
00:10:41,033 --> 00:10:42,467
Please, believe me.

187
00:10:42,600 --> 00:10:46,133
Give me another chance.

188
00:10:46,267 --> 00:10:50,433
[SOBBING]

189
00:10:50,567 --> 00:10:51,367
[SLAPS]

190
00:10:53,400 --> 00:10:55,033
If you are such
a disappointment,

191
00:10:55,167 --> 00:10:57,433
then I wouldn't end up
with your sibling.

192
00:10:57,567 --> 00:10:58,833
You're a liar!

193
00:10:58,967 --> 00:10:59,967
You're such a cheater!

194
00:11:00,100 --> 00:11:01,967
Dad, stop it!

195
00:11:02,100 --> 00:11:03,567
Stop!

196
00:11:04,633 --> 00:11:05,800
What's going on?

197
00:11:06,967 --> 00:11:09,267
So, you cheated on Dad?

198
00:11:09,433 --> 00:11:12,300
You promised you
wouldn't hurt me.

199
00:11:13,933 --> 00:11:16,833
You promised a
strong relationship.

200
00:11:17,833 --> 00:11:22,667
That we are going to have
a complate family.

201
00:11:22,800 --> 00:11:27,400
But you were the one
who destroyed our family.

202
00:11:27,533 --> 00:11:30,667
And our family will be destroyed
bacause of you!

203
00:11:36,633 --> 00:11:38,067
Child, I'll explain.

204
00:11:38,200 --> 00:11:40,333
Answer my question!

205
00:11:40,467 --> 00:11:42,433
How could you do this to us?

206
00:11:42,833 --> 00:11:44,633
How could you ruin our lives?

207
00:11:44,767 --> 00:11:48,467
[DRAMATIC]

208
00:11:48,600 --> 00:11:49,467
Ashley!

209
00:12:08,467 --> 00:12:09,833
Forgive me.

210
00:12:11,000 --> 00:12:12,833
I regret everything.

211
00:12:12,967 --> 00:12:14,367
Please, forgive me.

212
00:12:14,500 --> 00:12:18,367
No matter how many times
I will never believe you again.

213
00:12:19,800 --> 00:12:22,000
I regret marrying you.

214
00:12:23,167 --> 00:12:25,200
I regret loving you.

215
00:12:25,333 --> 00:12:27,733
I regret ever knowing you!

216
00:12:27,867 --> 00:12:30,533
[DRAMATIC]

217
00:12:31,267 --> 00:12:32,667
Please, please.

218
00:12:33,667 --> 00:12:35,367
I know it's my fault.

219
00:12:35,500 --> 00:12:38,100
I know, I know it was wrong.

220
00:12:38,433 --> 00:12:39,867
But it's over now.

221
00:12:40,000 --> 00:12:41,967
Marj, please, let's fix this.

222
00:12:42,100 --> 00:12:43,233
Let's fix this.

223
00:12:43,367 --> 00:12:44,467
[SOBBING]

224
00:12:44,600 --> 00:12:47,933
What can be fixed
are unintended mistakes.

225
00:12:48,100 --> 00:12:50,267
But what you did, you chose it.

226
00:12:50,400 --> 00:12:51,567
You chose it!

227
00:12:53,833 --> 00:12:55,133
Marj, please.

228
00:12:55,267 --> 00:13:00,067
For our family, for our child,
I'm begging you.

229
00:13:00,200 --> 00:13:03,500
Don't drag our child into this,
Paolo.

230
00:13:03,633 --> 00:13:04,667
You didn't even think of her

231
00:13:04,800 --> 00:13:07,233
day after day
when you didn't come home

232
00:13:07,367 --> 00:13:08,867
because you were hiding
something!

233
00:13:09,000 --> 00:13:10,200
[SOBBING]

234
00:13:12,600 --> 00:13:13,267
Fine.

235
00:13:15,600 --> 00:13:17,333
Pour all your anger onto me.

236
00:13:17,467 --> 00:13:18,500
Hurt me!

237
00:13:18,633 --> 00:13:20,133
Slap me again!

238
00:13:21,767 --> 00:13:23,400
Just so you'll forgive me again.

239
00:13:23,533 --> 00:13:24,700
Don't touch me!

240
00:13:25,967 --> 00:13:28,600
No matter how many times
you kneel before me,

241
00:13:28,733 --> 00:13:31,100
you're not the only
one at fault here.

242
00:13:31,933 --> 00:13:33,367
You had an accomplice.

243
00:13:34,667 --> 00:13:37,233
You didn't just destroy
a relationship, Paolo.

244
00:13:37,367 --> 00:13:38,567
You destroyed my trust

245
00:13:38,700 --> 00:13:40,467
and one by one you will be held
accountable.

246
00:13:41,200 --> 00:13:43,833
Starting with you
and that shameless Thea.

247
00:13:43,967 --> 00:13:45,867
[DRAMATIC]

248
00:13:51,967 --> 00:13:53,033
Excuse me.

249
00:13:53,167 --> 00:13:54,800
Your cars are parked over there.

250
00:13:54,967 --> 00:13:57,000
- Thank you.
- All right.

251
00:13:57,133 --> 00:13:57,833
Ms. Yolly!

252
00:14:00,033 --> 00:14:01,133
Most of the guests have
already left,

253
00:14:01,267 --> 00:14:02,167
but I wasn't able to check

254
00:14:02,300 --> 00:14:04,800
if they deleted the video
from earlier.

255
00:14:04,933 --> 00:14:07,967
There's no point
even if you chase after them.

256
00:14:08,100 --> 00:14:10,500
The stench has already spread.

257
00:14:10,633 --> 00:14:14,200
Oh, Ms. Yolly, it might already
be posted on social media.

258
00:14:14,333 --> 00:14:17,067
These employers of ours
are so reckless.

259
00:14:18,400 --> 00:14:20,700
You know, if I were Ma'am Marj,

260
00:14:20,833 --> 00:14:22,667
that wouldn't be all Ma'am Thea
would get.

261
00:14:22,800 --> 00:14:23,600
I wouldn't just shove her

262
00:14:23,733 --> 00:14:25,100
into that cake that looks like
a coffin.

263
00:14:25,233 --> 00:14:27,067
After all, you took a mistress

264
00:14:27,200 --> 00:14:28,700
inside your own home
with your spouse.

265
00:14:28,867 --> 00:14:29,900
Exactly.

266
00:14:30,033 --> 00:14:32,033
But she shouldn't have done it
in front of the guests.

267
00:14:34,967 --> 00:14:35,833
Why not?

268
00:14:35,967 --> 00:14:38,833
Did Sir Paolo and Ma'am Thea
feel ashamed

269
00:14:38,967 --> 00:14:41,867
when they did their affair here?

270
00:14:43,200 --> 00:14:45,633
This house has been rotting
for a long time.

271
00:14:46,900 --> 00:14:49,200
There has long been
something rotten here.

272
00:14:49,933 --> 00:14:52,867
It was just covered up
by expensive curtains

273
00:14:53,000 --> 00:14:54,300
and chandeliers.

274
00:14:55,667 --> 00:14:58,000
Only now has the
stench truly spread.

275
00:14:59,533 --> 00:15:03,967
But Ms. Yolly, do you really
have no concern left

276
00:15:04,133 --> 00:15:05,167
for our employers?

277
00:15:05,300 --> 00:15:08,700
Don't you feel any pity
for what's happening to them?

278
00:15:08,833 --> 00:15:11,200
Why should I pity them?

279
00:15:11,333 --> 00:15:12,800
Did they ever pity me?

280
00:15:14,233 --> 00:15:17,767
Forty years I served them.

281
00:15:17,900 --> 00:15:20,267
I gave them my entire life.

282
00:15:20,400 --> 00:15:22,600
I made one mistake

283
00:15:22,733 --> 00:15:25,933
and they were eager to throw me
away like garbage.

284
00:15:26,067 --> 00:15:29,133
And now? And you ask me
to feel pity?

285
00:15:29,267 --> 00:15:30,633
I don't care anymore

286
00:15:30,767 --> 00:15:33,167
even if they all kill each other
inside!

287
00:15:41,867 --> 00:15:43,500
That Paolo is truly greedy.

288
00:15:44,733 --> 00:15:46,333
He wants to take everything
from me.

289
00:15:47,967 --> 00:15:49,700
I could have understood
when he took Marj from me,

290
00:15:49,833 --> 00:15:51,600
but now, even my spouse.

291
00:15:51,933 --> 00:15:54,567
He even messed with my wife!

292
00:15:54,700 --> 00:15:55,933
What kind of sibling does that?

293
00:15:56,067 --> 00:15:56,933
I will never forgive that.

294
00:15:57,067 --> 00:15:58,900
- I'll kill him!
- Edward, Edward, Edward.

295
00:15:59,033 --> 00:15:59,833
Enough.

296
00:15:59,967 --> 00:16:00,933
Paolo is still
your older sibling.

297
00:16:01,067 --> 00:16:02,100
You shouldn't be fighting.

298
00:16:02,233 --> 00:16:03,700
What sibling? What sibling, Mom?

299
00:16:05,000 --> 00:16:07,200
No sibling would ever do
that to their own family!

300
00:16:09,167 --> 00:16:10,700
Mom, I was humiliated!

301
00:16:11,867 --> 00:16:14,533
They messed with me with Thea,
Marj and me.

302
00:16:24,000 --> 00:16:27,067
Do not ever go against
your brother

303
00:16:27,200 --> 00:16:29,033
if you don't want us
to have problems.

304
00:16:30,167 --> 00:16:32,000
Are you serious, Dad?

305
00:16:32,133 --> 00:16:34,933
You're still siding with Paolo
even though I'm the one wronged?

306
00:16:36,800 --> 00:16:38,967
All my life,
it's always been Paolo!

307
00:16:39,967 --> 00:16:41,400
Paolo is the good one!

308
00:16:42,900 --> 00:16:43,767
I'm your child too!

309
00:16:43,900 --> 00:16:45,833
I wish for once you'd be fair!

310
00:16:47,933 --> 00:16:49,700
- You're disrespectful!
- Enough, Greg!

311
00:16:52,067 --> 00:16:55,433
I can endure your
poor treatment of me.

312
00:16:56,900 --> 00:17:00,933
But the moment you hurt Edward,
I swear!

313
00:17:03,100 --> 00:17:05,400
We will leave you

314
00:17:05,533 --> 00:17:07,167
so the whole world will know

315
00:17:07,300 --> 00:17:10,733
how rotten this perfect family
truly is!

316
00:17:11,867 --> 00:17:12,867
[SOBBING]

317
00:17:13,000 --> 00:17:14,733
[INTENSE]

318
00:17:22,300 --> 00:17:23,633
Ashley.

319
00:17:23,767 --> 00:17:25,167
Ashley, wait.

320
00:17:26,500 --> 00:17:28,433
Wait, I'll explain.

321
00:17:28,567 --> 00:17:29,900
It wasn't like that.

322
00:17:30,033 --> 00:17:31,200
- Ashley!
- Can you stop it, Mom!

323
00:17:31,333 --> 00:17:32,300
Enough!

324
00:17:33,600 --> 00:17:36,900
This wasn't just
a misunderstanding.

325
00:17:37,033 --> 00:17:38,633
I heard everything.

326
00:17:39,700 --> 00:17:41,967
You chose to do this, Mom.

327
00:17:42,100 --> 00:17:43,300
I'll explain it to you.

328
00:17:43,433 --> 00:17:45,133
Don't use Dad as an excuse!

329
00:17:48,200 --> 00:17:50,367
Dad should not be
used as an excuse.

330
00:17:50,500 --> 00:17:52,800
He's not an excuse
to hurt the family!

331
00:17:54,567 --> 00:17:56,500
It's so wrong, Mom.

332
00:17:56,633 --> 00:17:58,700
Don't you know
that it's so wrong!

333
00:17:58,833 --> 00:18:00,100
Ashley, please.

334
00:18:00,233 --> 00:18:02,333
- Please listen to me...
- You're so disgusting!

335
00:18:03,867 --> 00:18:05,167
Ashley! Wait!

336
00:18:05,300 --> 00:18:06,367
Don't touch me!

337
00:18:09,533 --> 00:18:10,800
Get out of my way.

338
00:18:12,167 --> 00:18:15,100
Don't expect your child
to forgive you anymore.

339
00:18:15,233 --> 00:18:17,833
She already saw what kind
of monster her mother is.

340
00:18:19,167 --> 00:18:20,333
[SOBBING]

341
00:18:26,433 --> 00:18:27,567
Ash?

342
00:18:27,700 --> 00:18:28,533
[SOBBING]

343
00:18:28,667 --> 00:18:32,400
[DRAMATIC]

344
00:18:32,533 --> 00:18:34,633
[SOBBING]

345
00:18:39,667 --> 00:18:40,767
Sorry.

346
00:18:42,200 --> 00:18:44,567
Everything is
already so messy.

347
00:18:44,700 --> 00:18:46,167
I don't know what to say.

348
00:18:46,300 --> 00:18:48,767
You don't have to say anything.

349
00:18:48,900 --> 00:18:49,900
The guests are leaving.

350
00:18:52,533 --> 00:18:54,033
Grandma and I are going home
too.

351
00:18:56,533 --> 00:19:01,133
But it doesn't feel right
to leave with you like this.

352
00:19:04,000 --> 00:19:05,900
I'm sorry about what happened.

353
00:19:06,033 --> 00:19:08,400
I'm sorry you had to witness
that, Ashley.

354
00:19:11,467 --> 00:19:13,067
I'm sorry I ever had to see
that.

355
00:19:14,933 --> 00:19:17,100
Earlier I thought it
was just a glitch.

356
00:19:18,967 --> 00:19:20,300
No. It was real.

357
00:19:21,667 --> 00:19:23,500
All this time,

358
00:19:23,633 --> 00:19:25,967
my family has long been broken.

359
00:19:27,833 --> 00:19:29,733
They kept it going even
though it was broken.

360
00:19:30,967 --> 00:19:32,200
What will happen?

361
00:19:33,867 --> 00:19:36,233
I don't even know
if Jasmine knows about this.

362
00:19:36,367 --> 00:19:38,200
What will happen if Jasmine
finds out, right?

363
00:19:38,333 --> 00:19:39,667
They lied to us, Xander!

364
00:19:39,800 --> 00:19:42,800
My family is a bunch of liars!

365
00:19:42,933 --> 00:19:43,767
Move aside!

366
00:19:43,900 --> 00:19:45,833
You leave this place!

367
00:19:45,967 --> 00:19:49,733
Snakes and traitors like you
have no place in this house.

368
00:19:49,867 --> 00:19:52,967
Stay away and don't ever
come back!

369
00:19:53,100 --> 00:19:54,567
You're kicking me out?

370
00:19:54,700 --> 00:19:57,900
Who are you to tell me
where I can go?

371
00:19:58,033 --> 00:20:01,533
I'm just the spouse
you chose to be with.

372
00:20:01,700 --> 00:20:03,867
The family you destroyed.

373
00:20:04,000 --> 00:20:05,533
You are poison.

374
00:20:05,667 --> 00:20:06,533
So, leave now from here

375
00:20:06,667 --> 00:20:09,433
before everyone else
gets infected.

376
00:20:09,567 --> 00:20:11,500
Don't forget, Marj.

377
00:20:11,633 --> 00:20:13,533
I am also a Torrecampo's spouse.

378
00:20:13,667 --> 00:20:15,600
My child is also an heir.

379
00:20:15,733 --> 00:20:16,967
Ashley and I are not leaving

380
00:20:17,100 --> 00:20:19,833
because we have rights to this
house and to the company.

381
00:20:19,967 --> 00:20:21,667
You have some nerve.

382
00:20:21,800 --> 00:20:23,900
You're unbelievably shameless.

383
00:20:24,033 --> 00:20:26,633
After destroying this family,

384
00:20:26,767 --> 00:20:29,533
you're still thinking about
inheritance?

385
00:20:29,667 --> 00:20:32,700
You're not just shameless,
you're money-hungry.

386
00:20:33,433 --> 00:20:34,533
Why?

387
00:20:34,700 --> 00:20:38,367
Do you think if I leave,
you and Paolo will fix things?

388
00:20:40,033 --> 00:20:42,000
You're blaming me too much.

389
00:20:42,133 --> 00:20:45,667
I'm not the only reason
you fell apart.

390
00:20:45,800 --> 00:20:49,033
From the start, you and Paolo
were bound to fail.

391
00:20:50,867 --> 00:20:52,167
You know what?

392
00:20:52,300 --> 00:20:56,667
I can't blame why the two
siblings went crazy over me.

393
00:20:56,800 --> 00:20:58,500
[LAUGHS]

394
00:20:58,633 --> 00:21:00,033
Crazy, right?

395
00:21:00,167 --> 00:21:02,367
Which means, if they want
someone to stay

396
00:21:02,500 --> 00:21:04,467
in this house, it's me.

397
00:21:04,600 --> 00:21:08,300
And if they want someone gone,
it's you!

398
00:21:09,800 --> 00:21:11,000
[SLAPS]

399
00:21:11,133 --> 00:21:13,933
[CLAMORING]

400
00:21:14,067 --> 00:21:19,467
[CLAMORING]

401
00:21:19,800 --> 00:21:21,733
Thea! Stop it!

402
00:21:21,867 --> 00:21:23,333
[THUDS]

403
00:21:23,467 --> 00:21:25,133
[GRUNTS]

404
00:21:25,267 --> 00:21:26,633
Stop it!

405
00:21:26,967 --> 00:21:27,967
You shameless woman!

406
00:21:30,133 --> 00:21:31,333
You should be dead!

407
00:21:31,467 --> 00:21:32,500
[CLAMORING]

408
00:21:32,633 --> 00:21:34,467
They lied to me!

409
00:21:34,600 --> 00:21:36,867
They lied to me, Xander!

410
00:21:38,000 --> 00:21:39,167
[DRAMATIC]

411
00:21:39,300 --> 00:21:41,433
They're all liars.

412
00:21:43,000 --> 00:21:49,467
[SOBBING]

413
00:21:49,600 --> 00:21:50,500
Don't say that.

414
00:21:52,033 --> 00:21:53,100
Perhaps they lied

415
00:21:54,533 --> 00:21:56,533
because they were hiding
that things weren't working.

416
00:21:57,433 --> 00:22:02,200
You know, I thought we
were immune to this mess.

417
00:22:03,300 --> 00:22:04,400
But we weren't.

418
00:22:07,400 --> 00:22:09,833
Ash, no one is really immune.

419
00:22:10,600 --> 00:22:13,200
There are some things we
can't stop from happening.

420
00:22:13,333 --> 00:22:15,667
You don't have to figure
this out tonight.

421
00:22:15,833 --> 00:22:17,567
You don't have to figure this
out alone.

422
00:22:18,333 --> 00:22:19,167
Xander.

423
00:22:21,467 --> 00:22:22,333
Thank you.

424
00:22:23,067 --> 00:22:25,433
Thank you for just
being here with me.

425
00:22:25,567 --> 00:22:26,700
[SIGHS]

426
00:22:28,933 --> 00:22:35,833
Do you really have any advice
for me to fix this?

427
00:22:35,967 --> 00:22:37,733
Even to make it better?

428
00:22:37,867 --> 00:22:39,667
I don't think this is the kind
of problem you fix

429
00:22:39,800 --> 00:22:40,867
on your own, Ashley.

430
00:22:42,433 --> 00:22:45,167
Especially since
it's not our fault.

431
00:22:46,033 --> 00:22:47,300
We just have to survive.

432
00:22:48,200 --> 00:22:49,733
I'll stay with you if you want.

433
00:22:51,367 --> 00:22:53,100
I'm here, Ashley.

434
00:22:53,233 --> 00:22:55,567
[DRAMATIC]

435
00:23:05,667 --> 00:23:06,500
Enough!

436
00:23:06,633 --> 00:23:07,467
Stop this!

437
00:23:08,933 --> 00:23:10,867
Enough!

438
00:23:11,000 --> 00:23:12,167
Edward!

439
00:23:12,300 --> 00:23:14,333
Stop it!

440
00:23:14,467 --> 00:23:15,600
Edward, stop it!

441
00:23:15,733 --> 00:23:17,067
You might kill your brother!

442
00:23:17,200 --> 00:23:18,433
Then let everyone die!

443
00:23:19,467 --> 00:23:20,667
So this can all end!

444
00:23:22,067 --> 00:23:23,400
To hell with this house!

445
00:23:24,233 --> 00:23:25,600
It's like this
family is cursed!

446
00:23:25,733 --> 00:23:26,867
It keeps repeating!

447
00:23:27,800 --> 00:23:31,867
This house and this family
should burn!

448
00:23:33,200 --> 00:23:35,167
Because this house
is hell itself!

449
00:23:37,800 --> 00:23:44,533
[INTENSE]

450
00:23:48,533 --> 00:23:51,400
Just stop it with this
violent nonsense!

451
00:23:51,800 --> 00:23:53,033
If you're going to act
like animals,

452
00:23:53,167 --> 00:23:54,700
at least do it with words!

453
00:23:55,967 --> 00:23:57,233
You know, we can
still fix this.

454
00:23:57,367 --> 00:23:58,967
But not if the two of you

455
00:23:59,100 --> 00:24:01,200
look like you're being dragged
out of a dark alley!

456
00:24:02,667 --> 00:24:04,400
You're right, Ma.

457
00:24:04,533 --> 00:24:05,300
I'm sorry.

458
00:24:05,433 --> 00:24:08,200
I was just trying
to defend myself.

459
00:24:08,333 --> 00:24:10,567
Don't you dare call her Mom!

460
00:24:10,700 --> 00:24:12,933
After you stabbed her children?

461
00:24:13,067 --> 00:24:14,333
You're disgusting!

462
00:24:16,400 --> 00:24:19,000
I'm sorry, Ma,
but I can't stay in this house

463
00:24:19,133 --> 00:24:20,533
while that woman is still here!

464
00:24:20,667 --> 00:24:21,433
Snake!

465
00:24:21,567 --> 00:24:23,767
Are you the owner of this house?

466
00:24:23,900 --> 00:24:26,633
Only Mom and Dad have the right
to kick me out,

467
00:24:26,767 --> 00:24:28,167
so, deal with it!

468
00:24:28,300 --> 00:24:28,967
Enough!

469
00:24:32,167 --> 00:24:33,167
No one is leaving.

470
00:24:34,600 --> 00:24:36,133
No one walks out.

471
00:24:36,267 --> 00:24:38,800
I don't want this scandal
to go public anymore.

472
00:24:39,967 --> 00:24:41,100
We contain it here.

473
00:24:43,333 --> 00:24:45,233
If someone needs to stay silent

474
00:24:45,467 --> 00:24:48,500
so the family won't
be humiliated further.

475
00:24:48,767 --> 00:24:52,300
Someone will stay quiet
and this ends here.

476
00:24:55,767 --> 00:24:58,200
That's it?

477
00:24:58,433 --> 00:25:00,500
We pretend nothing happened?

478
00:25:01,967 --> 00:25:06,167
I'm tired of this house
that can't even defend me.

479
00:25:06,733 --> 00:25:09,800
I'm tired of this family
that chooses silence

480
00:25:09,933 --> 00:25:12,400
and hides in this damn house

481
00:25:12,533 --> 00:25:15,567
just to protect its reputation
and avoid conflict.

482
00:25:16,867 --> 00:25:18,933
Marj, please, stop, please.

483
00:25:19,067 --> 00:25:22,600
If you can't remove that woman,
I will leave!

484
00:25:23,500 --> 00:25:25,367
And I will take my child
with me!

485
00:25:26,533 --> 00:25:29,600
I'm done with this family
and I'm done with you, Paolo!

486
00:25:29,733 --> 00:25:32,567
[INTENSE]

487
00:25:43,933 --> 00:25:49,100
Paolo, I'm afraid Marj
has opened a Pandora's Box.

488
00:25:49,233 --> 00:25:50,600
And you know what that means.

489
00:25:50,733 --> 00:25:53,000
Little by little,
the secrets of this house

490
00:25:53,133 --> 00:25:54,100
are coming out.

491
00:25:54,233 --> 00:25:57,400
No matter how much you clean,

492
00:25:57,533 --> 00:26:00,333
even if you close the doors
and the windows,

493
00:26:00,467 --> 00:26:04,867
you still can't stop the spread
of the lies of this house.

494
00:26:05,000 --> 00:26:06,333
What do you think will happen

495
00:26:06,467 --> 00:26:09,767
when Marj finds out that you've
been lying about Ashley,

496
00:26:09,933 --> 00:26:10,700
your child?

497
00:26:10,833 --> 00:26:12,133
That would be an
even bigger scandal.

498
00:26:12,267 --> 00:26:14,333
How many times
have you lied to me?

499
00:26:14,467 --> 00:26:16,000
Are you still hiding something?

500
00:26:16,133 --> 00:26:18,933
Because the moment I find out
you're still lying

501
00:26:19,067 --> 00:26:20,233
we're done, Paolo.

502
00:26:20,367 --> 00:26:23,900
And because I've long been a
witness to what happens here,

503
00:26:24,033 --> 00:26:26,933
I already know
when this will collapse.

504
00:26:27,267 --> 00:26:31,700
Even if you try to fix it,
it will fall on its own.

505
00:26:34,700 --> 00:26:36,500
Who did this?

506
00:26:36,633 --> 00:26:37,700
Who?
